tldr: The user wanted to improve the aesthetics of their sleep questionnaire
  app. I performed a comprehensive overhaul, introducing a calming sleep-themed
  color palette, refining UI components, and ensuring consistent styling across
  all sections to create a more professional and cohesive user experience.
overview: The user initiated a request to enhance the visual appeal of their
  sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was functional but lacked
  aesthetic polish. The approach involved a detailed analysis of the existing
  design, followed by a systematic implementation of improvements. Key decisions
  included transitioning to a calming, sleep-themed color palette, incorporating
  subtle background elements, and standardizing the styling of all UI components
  and form sections. This involved updating global CSS, the main questionnaire
  form, the intro section, and all individual form field components and content
  sections. The outcome is a significantly more polished, cohesive, and
  professional-looking application that effectively conveys a sense of calm and
  trustworthiness, aligning with the nature of a sleep health assessment. All
  changes were successfully implemented and verified without introducing new
  errors.
